Cell["\<\
Consider a mixed state of subsystem consisting of the first half of the \
fermion modes that results from tracing out the rest modes. The mixed state \
is characterized by the sub-block of the full matrix of Green's functions.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->1212757273,ExpressionUUID->"b6ad0189-8385-42f1-a669-c65de319fcc5"],

